# Security Triage (Weekly)

## Cadence

- Run `bash scripts/check-security-triage.sh --wait-ci 300` weekly (or `run-maintainer-gates.sh` full cycle)
- Triage OpenSSF Scorecard SARIF findings into BUILD_PLAN `[AGENT]` rows when not green

## Gates

- Zero open Critical/High Dependabot alerts before release (`pre-release-gate.sh`)
- Required workflows green: **CI**, **Security Scan**, **CodeQL**
- Scorecard workflow latest run should be `success` after `scorecard.yml` fix is on `main`

## gh auth

Dependabot API requires `gh` auth with access to repository security alerts. See `docs/SECURITY_TRIAGE.md`.
